

Bloodfist Help:  Gem Help File

To access information about a gem simply type:

    gemhelp <gemname>


Every gem should work with it's short description
as the <gemname>.

    gemhelp gem of speed


To simplify it though you can also use almost any
descriptive words in the gem name.  Basically you
can drop off words like 'gem', 'of', etc.

major gem of performance
    gemhelp major performance

gem of provoked aggression
    gemhelp provoked aggression

